---
import MarketingLayout from "../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
import FinalCTA from "../../components/sections/FinalCTA.astro";
---
<MarketingLayout title="About — Madar AI" description="We are building the AI Growth Operating System for subscription mobile apps.">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="section-badge">Our Story</div>
      <h1 class="about-headline">We built the tool<br/><span class="gradient-text">we always needed.</span></h1>
      <p class="about-sub">Every founder on our team has spent nights staring at 5 different dashboards trying to figure out why ROAS dropped, where churn is coming from, and what to do next. We built Madar AI so nobody has to do that again.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mission-section">
    <div class="ms-inner">
      <div class="ms-grid">
        <div class="ms-card">
          <div class="ms-icon">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="ms-title">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="ms-text">Make AI-powered growth intelligence accessible to every mobile app founder — not just those who can afford a Head of Growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ms-card">
          <div class="ms-icon">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="ms-title">Our Market</h3>
          <p class="ms-text">We focus on MENA, Turkey, and EU — markets where mobile app growth is exploding but tooling lags far behind Silicon Valley.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ms-card">
          <div class="ms-icon">🏗️</div>
          <h3 class="ms-title">Our Approach</h3>
          <p class="ms-text">Not a chatbot. Not a dashboard. A full AI Operating System with 12 specialized agents — each with memory, context, and execution capability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="values-section">
    <div class="vs-inner">
      <div class="section-badge-light">Values</div>
      <h2 class="vs-headline">How we work</h2>
      <div class="vs-list">
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-num">01</span><div><h4 class="vs-title">Ship fast, learn faster</h4><p class="vs-text">We ship every week. Real users beat perfect designs.</p></div></div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-num">02</span><div><h4 class="vs-title">Data is truth</h4><p class="vs-text">Every decision — product or business — is grounded in evidence, not opinion.</p></div></div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-num">03</span><div><h4 class="vs-title">Async by default</h4><p class="vs-text">We are fully remote across 4 timezones. Deep work is protected.</p></div></div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-num">04</span><div><h4 class="vs-title">Customer obsession</h4><p class="vs-text">We talk to users every week. Their problems are our roadmap.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="parent-section">
    <div class="ps-inner">
      <p class="ps-text">Madar AI is a product of</p>
      <a href="https://zyrix.com" class="ps-logo" target="_blank">Zyrix Global Technologies</a>
      <p class="ps-sub">Building AI-powered products for the next generation of digital businesses across MENA, Turkey, and Europe.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <FinalCTA />
</MarketingLayout>
<style>
.about-hero { padding: 120px 24px 80px; background: linear-gradient(180deg,#0F1117,#141929); text-align: center; }
.about-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
.section-badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #F97316; background: rgba(249,115,22,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.25); padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.about-headline { font-size: clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem); font-weight: 800; color: white; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.about-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height: 1.7; }
.mission-section { padding: 80px 24px; background: white; }
.ms-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
.ms-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 24px; }
.ms-card { padding: 32px; background: #F8F9FA; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 16px; }
.ms-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.ms-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.ms-text { font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.6; }
.values-section { padding: 80px 24px; background: #0F1117; }
.vs-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
.section-badge-light { display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #F97316; background: rgba(249,115,22,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.25); padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.vs-headline { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.vs-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
.vs-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px; padding: 24px; background: #161B26; border: 1px solid #2A3650; border-radius: 12px; }
.vs-num { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; font-family: monospace; color: #F97316; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 2px; }
.vs-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.vs-text { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.6; }
.parent-section { padding: 60px 24px; background: #141929; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #2A3650; }
.ps-inner { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
.ps-text { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.ps-logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #7C3AED; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ps-logo:hover { color: #22D3EE; }
.ps-sub { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); line-height: 1.6; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .ms-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
